quran[32]{c,v,t}:
  35,41,"Toto Nyasaye niye wikalilanga likulu nende ashialo bikhaye okhurulaho ne nibirulaho abulaho wakhabiikalila halali Ye, toto ye ni Omuholo muno Omunji Wobulesheli"
  35,42,"Ne betsuba khu Nyasaye eshitsubo shiabu eshikhongo mbu: “Omwikanyilisi nabetsela mbu balaba abalunjifu muno okhushilakhwo omukanda kundi kwosi kwosi.” Ne olwa Omwikanyilisi yaboolela shiyabametela shiosi shiosi tawe halali obukhayi"
  35,43,"Khulwa okhufura khwabu khushialo, nende okhukhola ebifwanga ebibii ne ebifwanga ebibii shibikalushilanga halali khu ulia wabikhola. Ne shibalindanga tawe halali omulukha kwa balia abaranjilila khale, ne sholanyoola abukabukhani khumilukha chia Nyasaye tawe, nohomba sholanyoola abukalukhasio khumilukha chia Nyasaye tawe"
  35,44,"Koo shibachendangakhwo khushialo mana balolakhwo shinga indukho yabalia bali imbeli wabu yali irie, ne bali nende amani muno okhushila bo? Ne shibulaho shinyala okhushila Nyasaye mwikulu nende khushialo. Toto ye ni Omumanyi muno Omunyali po"
  35,45,"Ne Nyasaye abukulilanga Abandu khukabakholanga , shiyakhaleshelekhwo khushialo khuno isolo yosiyosi tawe, halali ababikhanga okhula ebise biarebwaho, ne olwebise biabu biliula (balirungwa) toto Nyasaye alolanga muno Abasumba bebe"
  36,1,Ya-Sin
  36,2,Nditsuba khu Ikurani yamachesi
  36,3,Toto ewe oli mulala Khubarumwa
  36,4,Khunjila ingololofu
  36,5,Okhwishia khwa Nyasaye Owamani Owobukoosia muno
  36,6,Mbukho wikanyilisie Abandu ba Basamwana balekanyilisibwa tawe mana nabo bali mubukoyani
  36,7,"Obwatoto likhuwa liamala okhubura khubaanji mubo, mana shibasuubilanga tawe"
  36,8,"Toto efwe khwaboya mwikosi mwabu nemikoye okhuula khubinwanwa, mana emirwe chiabu chilisa hekulu"
  36,9,"Mana nikhura imbeli wabu eshikalilo nende inyuma wabu eshikalilo, mana nikhufunikha tsimoni tsiabu mana shibalolanga tawe"
  36,10,"Ne nihalalasa awo khubo, nobekanyilisia nohomba obule okhubekanyilisia , shibalisuubila tawe"
  36,11,"Toto ewe wikanyilisinjia ulia uloondanga ametsulisio mana naria Nyasaye Wetsimbabaasi, khukefisile, kho musuubisie eshileshelo nende omurungo omulayi"
  36,12,"Toto efwe khulamusinjia abafu, ne khuhandikanga kabakholanga nende kabalekha inyuma. Ne buli eshindu khwashibikha mushitabu shinoosinjia"
  36,13,"Ne bakanile imbakha nobachelasilia , Abandu bolukongo olwa betselwa nende Abarumwa"
  36,14,"Olwa khwabarumila babili, nibabayingasia mana nikhubametela owakhataru nibaboola mbu: “ toto efwe khurumilwe khinywe.”"
  36,15,"Nibaboola mbu: “enywe mulisa Abandu shinga efwe, ne (Nyasaye) Omunji Wetsimbabaasi shiyeshiakhwo shiosi shiosi tawe, ne enywe mukatinjia butswa.”"
  36,16,"Baboola mbu: “Nyasaye wefu Omulesi amanyile mbu efwe toto khurumilwe khwinywe"
  36,17,Nekhubula elindi tawe halali okhusia likhuwa lili habulafu
  36,18,"Baboola mbu: “efwe khubekongola nimulalekhana ninafu tawe khulabalasa amachina ne mulanyoola eshinyasio eshikhongo okhurula khwifwe.”"
  36,19,"Baboola mbu : “obubii bwenyu buli khwinywe, Shichila okhwitsulisibwa butswa, nohomba enywe muli Abandu babura eshichelo?”"
  36,20,"Mana Omundu mulala niyetsa okhurula mumbeka wolukongo nayuukanga naboola mbu: “enywe Abandu banje muloonde Abarumwa bano.”"
  36,21,"Muloonde balia abalabasaba omurungo tawe, nabo abeene nabalunjifu"
  36,22,Ne khulwa shina ndalalaama ulia wanoonga ne ewuwe namulikalusibwa
  36,23,Koo endiile Abanyasaye bandi balali Ye. Omunji wetsimbabaasi niyanyenyela amabii okhusaba khwenyu shikhukhoonya shiosi shiosi tawe nohomba shibakhahabina tawe
  36,24,Toto mana esie endio emba endi mubukori bwa habulafu
  36,25,Toto esie usuubiile khu Nyasaye wenyu omulesi kho murechelesie
  36,26,"Naboolelwa mbu ; “injila mwikulu,” naboola mbu : “ Abayie Abandu banje bamanyanga khwo"
  36,27,Shingala Nyasaye wanje Omulesi yandesheele mana niyanda mubalia boluyali.”